{"arkId":"cl010099903","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099903","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1625","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1625,"imprecision":"","text":"1er quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Cameel, Caspar","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8292","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond du bo\u00eetier serti d\u0027une agate grav\u00e9e d\u0027une ronde champ\u00eatre rythm\u00e9e par le son d\u0027une cornemuse et \u00e0 l\u0027arri\u00e8re-plan un hallali de cerf ; m\u00e9daillon encadr\u00e9 de huit brillants s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des arceaux d\u00e9coup\u00e9s \u00e0 jour et recouverts d\u0027\u00e9mail opaque bleu et blanc. Carrure d\u00e9cor\u00e9e de sept brillants sertis dans des montures en forme de fleurs se d\u00e9tachant sur un fond opaque bleu clair et s\u00e9par\u00e9es par des losanges en pointill\u00e9s ; m\u00eame d\u00e9cor sur la lunette du verre. Int\u00e9rieur de la cuvette pr\u00e9sentant un motif floral bleu opaque et vert translucide. Charni\u00e8re au-dessus du XII, pendant en forme de bouton de fleur laissant librement passer l\u0027anneau de suspension. Cadran en laiton \u00e0 chiffres romains, d\u00e9cor\u00e9 en \u00e9maux translucides et opaques de fleurettes et tiges formant de d\u00e9licates arabesques o\u00f9 apparaissent deux insectes affront\u00e9s. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre et une fus\u00e9e (corde \u00e0 boyau manquante). Le coq ovale \u00e0 un pied et le cliquet grav\u00e9s et reperc\u00e9s de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Caspar Cameel\/a Strasb\u00fcrg","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,3","displayDimension":"4,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2","displayDimension":"2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : agate\r\nMat\u00e9riau : diamant\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Strasbourg (Alsace-\u003EBas-Rhin)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 885 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","